  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5389276">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5389276/" class="title-link">这本书的优缺点</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5389276"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/HZL10086/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2621988-61.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/HZL10086/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">海之岚</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-04-15"
      class="main-meta">2012-04-15 03:44:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5389276_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这套书的弱点在于对美国的政治和经济写的不够深入，强项在于对社会以及丰富多彩的老百姓的日常生活，写的很好。这本书毕竟是历史教材，和中国的历史教材也类似，也强调美国自由平等这类价值观的灌输，但更加潜移默化不像中国的教材那么招人反感，反倒很吸引人。  同时这本书的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5389276_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5389276_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










